channel.title: Help going from Delta to PI
channel.description:
Hey guys, could someone help me with the basics of PI? for instance how to setup the cache? i have a PI source and i know the absolute basics which is literally the server basics in the config file, but apart from that im completely stuck.
can someone help me please? thanks :)

item.dc:creator: @Dan0194 Dan0194
item.description:
@Dan0194 wrote:

Well you should be having no problem client sided with the switch because whatever client you used for delta should work for P.I. as long as they are the same revision(or else you may experience some problems). And deltascape is the same as P.I. they are both programmed in java. You are just going to need to get used to where everything is in P.I. it wonâ€™t take you too long
